  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-10o75c2\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"o9VEUwuc\">换句话说，70万（仅评论区提醒，题主给出的是7万）就可以获得一套原装的、有感官的、正常分泌激素的、可以生育的、<span class=\"highlight-wrap other\" data-highlight-id=\"1760749526636646400\" data-highlight-split-type=\"both\" data-highlight-id-extra=\"\">没有排异反应</span>的器官。</p><p data-pid=\"Dzy1fnl2\">泰国有家专业中介叫<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=658054035&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E6%9B%BC%E8%B0%B7%E9%9B%A8&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">曼谷雨<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>，专门对接各国患者和医院，大概花费几十万人民币，只能获得<span class=\"highlight-wrap other\" data-highlight-id=\"1762220145450504192\" data-highlight-split-type=\"both\" data-highlight-id-extra=\"\">一套看起来像是，但不具备以上任何特性的器官</span>。</p><p data-pid=\"C4juwIj6\">你要是能提供这个服务，一年赚一个亿算我估计的保守了…</p></span><span id=\"VirtualCatalogAnchorPoint\"></span></span></div>",
